#: apps/raffle/models.py
msgid ""
"Fly with the corp, earn raffle tickets, win prizes. Connect your ESI token "
"and enrol in FORCA Command Grid to take part — only enrolled pilots with a "
"live ESI connection can earn tickets and win."
msgstr ""
"Летайте с корпорацией, зарабатывайте лотерейные билеты, выигрывайте призы. "
