"Each card previews its would-be live score now; enabling one adds it to the "
"index at the recommended starter weight. Fine-tune weights and bands "
"afterwards on <a href=\"%(url)s\" class=\"text-cyan "
"hover:underline\">Dimensions &amp; weights</a>."
